People who need their stuff to be carried are always existed. Unfortunately, it is not always easy to find a carrier as they wanted. Instead of traditional methods, we provide a service that gathers customers and carriers easily.

Aim of the Project and Justification
•	Offering variety of carriers
•	Providing special service as customer’s need
•	Creating a platform for carrying area
•	Forcing carriers to compete
Necessity of the Project
•	There is no application for only carrying
•	Other applications do not focus on carrying
Application
•	Reaches users via android application
•	Users are separated as customers and carriers
•	Carriers create notices and specifies their schedules, prices and locations
•	Customers searches among carriers 
•	Application shows available carriers and their specifications
•	Customer get contact with carrier
